#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn20.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn20.12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 20 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 20 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.12:0.2"
msgid "1. Opammavagga "
msgstr "1. Similes "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn20.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Dutiyasiṅgālasutta "
msgstr "12. A Jackal (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn20.12:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.12:1.2"
msgid "“Assuttha no tumhe, bhikkhave, rattiyā paccūsasamayaṃ jarasiṅgālassa vassamānassā”ti? "
msgstr "“Mendicants, did you hear an old jackal howling at the crack of dawn?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.12:1.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.12:1.4"
msgid "“Siyā kho, bhikkhave, tasmiṃ jarasiṅgāle yā kāci kataññutā kataveditā, na tveva idhekacce sakyaputtiyapaṭiññe siyā yā kāci kataññutā kataveditā. "
msgstr "“There might be some gratitude and thankfulness in that old jackal, but there is none in a certain person here who claims to be a follower of the Sakyan son. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.12:1.5"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "So you should train like this: "

msgctxt "sn20.12:1.6"
msgid "‘kataññuno bhavissāma katavedino; "
msgstr "‘We will be grateful and thankful. "

#. VAR: no → na ca noti idaṃ bj, pts1-2 potthakesu
#. VAR: nassissatī’ti → mā nassissatīti (bj, pts1-2) | ca na sissatīti (s1) | vinasissatīti (s2, s3, km)
msgctxt "sn20.12:1.7"
msgid "na ca no amhesu appakampi kataṃ nassissatī’ti. "
msgstr "We won’t forget even a small thing done for us.’ "

msgctxt "sn20.12:1.8"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how you should train.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn20.12:1.9"
msgid "Dvādasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn20.12:1.10"
msgid "Opammavaggo paṭhamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn20.12:2.1"
msgid "Kūṭaṃ nakhasikhaṃ kulaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn20.12:2.2"
msgid "okkhā satti dhanuggaho; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn20.12:2.3"
msgid "Āṇi kaliṅgaro nāgo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn20.12:2.4"
msgid "biḷāro dve siṅgālakāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn20.12:2.5"
msgid "Opammasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ. "
msgstr "The Linked Discourses with similes are complete."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
